trans-unit.source: Provides the managed definition of the <see langword="IEnumFORMATETC" /> interface.
trans-unit.target: 提供 <see langword="IEnumFORMATETC" /> 介面的 Managed 定義。

trans-unit.source: This interface enumerates an array of <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.ComTypes.FORMATETC> structures.
trans-unit.target: 這個介面會列舉陣列<xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.ComTypes.FORMATETC>結構。

trans-unit.source: For more information about the `IEnumFORMATETC` interface, see the MSDN Library.
trans-unit.target: 如需有關`IEnumFORMATETC`介面，請參閱 MSDN Library。

trans-unit.source: The common language runtime throws an exception when a COM method in native code returns an HRESULT.
trans-unit.target: 原生程式碼的 COM 方法傳回的 HRESULT 時，common language runtime 會擲回例外狀況。

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [How to: Map HRESULTs and Exceptions](~/docs/framework/interop/how-to-map-hresults-and-exceptions.md).
trans-unit.target: 如需詳細資訊，請參閱[如何： 對應 Hresult 和例外狀況](~/docs/framework/interop/how-to-map-hresults-and-exceptions.md)。

trans-unit.source: When this method returns, contains a reference to the newly created enumerator.
trans-unit.target: 這個方法傳回時，包含新建列舉值的參考。

trans-unit.source: This parameter is passed uninitialized.
trans-unit.target: 這個參數會以未初始化的狀態傳遞。

trans-unit.source: Creates a new enumerator that contains the same enumeration state as the current enumerator.
trans-unit.target: 建立新的列舉值，其包含與目前列舉值相同的列舉型別 (Enumeration) 狀態。

trans-unit.source: For more information about `IEnumFORMATETC::Clone`, see the MSDN Library.
trans-unit.target: 如需有關`IEnumFORMATETC::Clone`，請參閱 MSDN Library。

trans-unit.source: The number of <see cref="T:System.Runtime.InteropServices.ComTypes.FORMATETC" /> references to return in <c>rgelt</c>.
trans-unit.target: 要在 <c>rgelt</c> 中傳回之 <see cref="T:System.Runtime.InteropServices.ComTypes.FORMATETC" /> 參考的數目。

trans-unit.source: When this method returns, contains a reference to the enumerated <see cref="T:System.Runtime.InteropServices.ComTypes.FORMATETC" /> references.
trans-unit.target: 當這個方法傳回時，會包含列舉之 <see cref="T:System.Runtime.InteropServices.ComTypes.FORMATETC" /> 參考的參考。

trans-unit.source: This parameter is passed uninitialized.
trans-unit.target: 這個參數會以未初始化的狀態傳遞。

trans-unit.source: When this method returns, contains a reference to the actual number of references enumerated in <c>rgelt</c>.
trans-unit.target: 當這個方法傳回時，會包含 <c>rgelt</c> 所列舉之參考實際數目的參考。

trans-unit.source: This parameter is passed uninitialized.
trans-unit.target: 這個參數會以未初始化的狀態傳遞。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves a specified number of items in the enumeration sequence.
trans-unit.target: 擷取列舉型別序列中指定的項目數目。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="S_OK" /> if the <paramref name="pceltFetched" /> parameter equals the <paramref name="celt" /> parameter; otherwise, <see langword="S_FALSE" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果 <paramref name="pceltFetched" /> 參數等於 <paramref name="celt" /> 參數，則為 <see langword="S_OK" />，否則為 <see langword="S_FALSE" />。

trans-unit.source: For more information about `IEnumFORMATETC::Next`, see the MSDN Library.
trans-unit.target: 如需有關`IEnumFORMATETC::Next`，請參閱 MSDN Library。

trans-unit.source: Resets the enumeration sequence to the beginning.
trans-unit.target: 將列舉序列重設為開頭。

trans-unit.source: An HRESULT with the value <see langword="S_OK" />.
trans-unit.target: HRESULT，擁有值 <see langword="S_OK" />。

trans-unit.source: For more information about `IEnumFORMATETC::Reset`, see the MSDN Library.
trans-unit.target: 如需有關`IEnumFORMATETC::Reset`，請參閱 MSDN Library。

trans-unit.source: The number of elements to skip in the enumeration.
trans-unit.target: 列舉型別中要略過的項目數。

trans-unit.source: Skips a specified number of items in the enumeration sequence.
trans-unit.target: 略過列舉序列中指定的項目數目。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="S_OK" /> if the number of elements skipped equals the <paramref name="celt" /> parameter; otherwise, <see langword="S_FALSE" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果略過的元素數目等於 <paramref name="celt" /> 參數，則為 <see langword="S_OK" />，否則為 <see langword="S_FALSE" />。

trans-unit.source: For more information about `IEnumFORMATETC::Skip`, see the MSDN Library.
trans-unit.target: 如需有關`IEnumFORMATETC::Skip`，請參閱 MSDN Library。
